http://www.geocities.com/Tokyo/Towers/9151/bushido.htm

Jin - compassion

Gi - honesty

Chu - loyalty

Ko - piety

Rei - courtesy

Chi - wisdom

Shin - sincerity

Tei -  Humanitarianism (roughly)

My Sensei believes they left out;

Yu - courage

Meyo - honor

This may be the most succinct "content" for Bushido one will find...
